  "label": "Sevrin Halor",
  "description": "This individual presents as an undead human, reduced to a gaunt frame with brown skin drawn tight over prominent cheekbones and jaw. Black hair persists in sparse, uneven growth, receding from a cracked scalp and exposing long-healed fractures across the crown. Brown eyes sit deep in the sockets and remain fixed and unblinking, lending the face an enduring, sepulchral stillness. The hands and forearms show persistent fissuring and mineral-stained scarring consistent with prolonged exposure to abrasive cavern stone and crystalline dust.",
